HEADWORD: Indubitably
<hw>In*du"bi*ta*bly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Undoubtedly;
unquestionably; in a manner to remove all doubt.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Oracles <qex>indubitably</qex> clear and infallibly certain.</q>
<rj><qau>Barrow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indubitate</ent>⟦br⟧
